  <ability>
    <abilitytitle>Flee</abilitytitle>
    <abilityid>physical.flee</abilityid>
    <abilityclass>Fast</abilityclass>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
        The Flee ability allows the character to move more than twice their movement rate
	away from an enemy, fear has given them wings.  Characters who are fleeing must
	make a Rally check in the End Stage to stop fleeing.  Characters may voluntarily
	flee if there exists a credible threat, or they may be forced to flee if they
	fail a break test.  For the purposes of game play fleeing is considered to be a
	double movement <emph>+d6</emph>.  Fleeing is successful if the character is not
	damaged in the following round.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
