  <ability>
    <abilitytitle>Head Butt</abilitytitle>
    <abilityid>physical.head_butt</abilityid>
    <abilityclass>Slow</abilityclass>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
	A head butt involves the attacker driving the top of their head into the bridge 
	of the defenders nose.  Head butting is mainly used as an attack of last resort or 
	as a surprise attack.  An attacker may only head butt someone immediately in 
	front or behind them.  An character may head butt when grappled.
      </p>

      <p>
	Head butts do +2 damage if the attacker is wearing a helmet and -2 damage
	if the defender is wearing a helmet.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
